Use the standard library
This is how to find_max of words:
   Remember that best is item 0 in words
   Remember that i is 1
   Do this (diff of words's length and 1) times:
      Remember that current is item i in words
      When current is more than best, then:
         Remember that best is current
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is best
